   "source": [
    "1. How do you distinguish between shutil.copy() and shutil.copytree()?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "9fe0cc87",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Ans:-\n",
    "    shutil.copy : Copies a single file.\n",
    "    shutil.copytree() : will copy an entire folder and every folder and file contained in it."
   ]
  },
